<item>
            <title>[SOLR-641] expose EmbeddedSolrServer response parsing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-641</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the EmbeddedSolrServer writes the response to XML (a string) then parses it so that it has an equivolent response to if it were passed around via HTTP.  We should:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;make this more efficient, or at least refactor so it is easy to make it more efficient in the future&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;expose the parsing functions, so other components could use it directly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
